HEADWORD: Stainer
<hw>Stain"er</hw> <pr>(-⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>One who stains or tarnishes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A workman who stains; <as>as, a <ex>stainer</ex> of
wood</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stainless</ent>⟦br⟧
